Subject: [PATCH 1/2] feat(teamver): Design Track A integration and storage
 launch-gate docs (staging)
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Prod 공개 출시 전 volume-only 배포가 blocker임을 문서화하고, S3 SSOT +
Litestream + design-api registry(Phase 0~3) 출시 게이트를 SSOT로 추가한다.
동시에 Teamver Design Track A(sidecar) 구현·runbook을 staging에 포함한다.

Documentation (docs-teamver):
- Add 09_Design_저장소_격리_출시게이트.md — Hybrid SSOT, Phase 0~4 진행 표,
  Acceptance Criteria, tenant isolation, Litestream; volume-only prod 금지
- Update 04_구현_우선순위 — storage/isolation을 Track A prod 필수로 재정의
- Update 00/03/05/07/README — 09 cross-link, 미완·체크리스트·scratch volume
- deploy/teamver/docs — TEAMVER_APPS_INTEGRATION, DEPLOY-AWS, SDK vendor runbook

deploy/teamver (design-api sidecar):
- FastAPI design-api: auth/session, bootstrap relay, usage/events, M2M token-usage
- teamver-app-sdk-python integration (teamver_sdk.py); Postgres schema bootstrap
- docker-compose (OD daemon + design-api + optional local-db), run_docker.sh
- nginx conf for stg-design* / design* (auth_request, OD_API_TOKEN)
- env examples (.env.staging/.production), deploy .gitignore

OD web embed (apps/web):
- @teamver/app-sdk BFF client, session banner, embed mode (designApiBase)
- TeamverSessionBanner, teamver.css; EntryShell wiring

Tooling:
- scripts/sync-teamver-vendor.sh, check-teamver-vendor.mjs
- packages/teamver-integration (Track B headless OdDaemonClient)
- vendor/teamver/README.md; root .gitignore for vendor binaries

Phase 0~3(09) 완료 전 Production 공개 오픈하지 않는다.

